    list: function(valueNames) {
        var listHtml = $('<div id="list-pagination"><ul class="list"></ul><ul class="pagination"></ul></div>'),
            item = "";
 
        item = "<li>";
        for (var i = 0; i < valueNames.length; i++) {
            item += '<span class="'+valueNames[i]+'"</span>';
        }
        item += "</li>";
